Fɛn bɛɛ tɛ a kɔnɔ wa kalanlenko tɛ.
A labɛnna ka sinsin baloko jogow kan walasa ka togodalamusow ni sannikɛlaw kunnafoni balofɛnw kunkankobaw kan, balofɛn minnu b'an bolokɔrɔ an ka sigida la ani minnu bɛɛ doni julabaw fɛ ka bɔ jamana wɛrɛw la ka na don an faso kɔnɔ.
Sigida balofɛn minnu ye sɛnɛtaw ye ani minnu tɛ sɛnɛ, olu suguya ka ca Mali la.
Damadɔ de tara an fɛ k'olu kɛ misaliw ye, k'u nafa n'u magoɲɛw jira baloko ɲuman sira fɛ.
Balofɛn minnu bɛ bɔ jamana wɛrɛw la ka don an ka suguw la, o dunfɛnw bɛ gɛlɛya ni kɔlɔlɔ minnu don an faso kɔnɔ, gafe in bɛ sinsin olu de kan.
