Kumaden-sugu kelen nali kɔrɔɲɔgɔnmaw bɛɛ la
O tusunsugu la, daɲɛ fɛn o fɛn Bɛ yen i b'a Sɔrɔ olu bɛɛ jɛ ye kumaden kelen ye ni k'u kumaden tɔw Kɛ sugubɛɛ-sugubɛɛ ye.
Kumaden minnu bɛ seginnkanni-kumaden in Dafa daɲɛw la, o kumadenw daɲɛnama de ye kɔrɔɲɔgɔnmaw ye (baganmara, bagannadon = mara, ladon).
