Daɲɛ-mɔɔnɔbɔ ka kɔrɔɲɔgɔnmaya bangelen
Daɲɛgana dɔw Bɛ yen minnu kɔrɔ ni u dorokolen kɔrɔ bɛɛ ye kelen ye daɲɛ dɔw la.
